TOCOM to raise January rubber futures margin fee . The Tokyo Commodity Exchange ( TOCOM ) said on Tuesday it would raise the margin requirement on its January rubber futures contract by 50 , 000 yen per trading lot , effective from Wednesday . The rise will bring the total January requirement to 127 , 750 yen , TOCOM said in a statement . The increase is intended to cool overheated trade . The requirement on other rubber contracts will be unchanged at 52 , 500 yen , TOCOM said . - - Tokyo Commodity Desk + 81 - 3 - 3432 - 7431 
